        "name": "Shifting Stance",
        "description": "After this monster successfully performs Counter using an Attack-type move once, it fully restores HP and transforms into 'Chess Queen'. After transforming, its base stats and trait become those of Chess Queen, while its equipped moves remain unchanged. The Attack and Defense bonuses gained before transformation persist after transforming. Before transformation, Chess Queen’s trait can already be triggered normally, and its effects will take effect after transformation.",
